      "post_date": "2024-12-12 11:39:04",
      "post_date_gmt": "2024-12-12 06:09:04",
      "post_content": "<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Yoga, the practice that emerged from ancient India has been merging and morphing with the changing socio-political-cultural landscape, to evolve as a framework for spiritual, emotional, and physical transformation through the ages. Undoubtedly, regular Yoga practice brings physical fitness, breath awareness, connection with the mind and finally the inner self.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>In all of this, the role of women in yoga – its evolution and development – has been a subject of keen interest and study.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Acknowledging this, today, we have with us Geetika Singh, a certified yoga instructor and fitness trainer, who has set out to encourage people to embark on the yogic journey to witness profound transformation and long-term sustainability.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":5} -->\n<h5 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-entrepreneurship-is-rewarding-but-demanding-keep-learning-and-evolving\">“Entrepreneurship is rewarding but demanding. Keep learning and evolving.”<\/h5>\n<!-- \/wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":5} -->\n<h5 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-ques-what-prompted-you-to-embark-on-the-entrepreneurial-journey\">Ques. What prompted you to embark on the entrepreneurial journey?<\/h5>\n<!-- \/wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Amidst the COVID chaos when daily lives were disrupted, I saw an opportunity to bring stability and healing through yoga. It’s a calling to spread wellness and mindfulness in the community, society and the entire world. My love for yoga and desire to make a positive impact on others' lives not just physically, but mentally and emotionally, drove me to take the leap and embark on my entrepreneurial journey.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":5} -->\n<h5 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-ques-what-challenges-did-you-face-while-spreading-your-wings-and-how-did-you-address-them\">Ques. What challenges did you face while spreading your wings and how did you address them?<\/h5>\n<!-- \/wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>There were many challenges; like, rapport building with clients, adopting to new technology and social media, and being constantly available for multiple clients was the biggest challenge of all.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>However, challenges are temporary – they come and go. With consistent effort and patience everything falls in place – this belief, coupled with self-motivation and determination, helped me to overcome challenges all the way.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Being a yoga enthusiast, I indeed love to assist everyone but I have my own set of boundaries and I strongly believe loving yourself and taking care of yourself should be one’s priority.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":5} -->\n<h5 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-ques-what-according-to-you-is-the-real-value-of-yoga-meditation-exercise\">Ques. What according to you is the real value of yoga\/meditation\/exercise?<\/h5>\n<!-- \/wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>To reflect the real value of these, I have taken the liberty of penning a verse: - <\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>In the quiet breath of morning's embrace, Yoga weaves peace, a gentle space.<\/em><\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>Meditation calms the tempest within,<\/em><\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>A haven of stillness, where clarity begins.<\/em><\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>Exercise fuels the body, mind, and soul,<\/em><\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>Together, they make us whole.<\/em><\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>Keeping all these three in place can help in bringing profound transformation and long-term<br>sustainability.<\/em><\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":5} -->\n<h5 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-ques-where-do-you-see-yourself-10-years-down-the-line\">Ques. Where do you see yourself 10 years down the line?<\/h5>\n<!-- \/wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>A few years down the line, I would continue to be deeply rooted with my yoga practice, striving to share its benefits with all. Yoga is a gateway to overall well-being and with continued learning, I envision to explore more areas of holistic wellness such as nutrition, deep meditation and even alternative healing practices. Possibly, I will be also be sharing my insights and experience through articles and journals in the near future.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The future holds endless possibilities, and with my continued enthusiasm, I’m sure to make a lasting impact in the world of yoga and beyond. I hope to live with more presence, peace and compassion. It will be a life -long journey.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":5} -->\n<h5 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-ques-any-words-of-wisdom-for-budding-women-entrepreneurs-who-wish-to-follow-in-your-footsteps\">Ques. Any words of wisdom for budding women entrepreneurs who wish to follow in your footsteps?<\/h5>\n<!-- \/wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Entrepreneurship is rewarding but demanding. Keep learning and evolving. Celebrate your uniqueness. Take one step at a time, and remain committed to your vision. Your resilience, passion and adaptability will be your greatest assets.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->",
